<br>
Scroll of Bristlebane's Bundle<br>
Scroll of Gift of Xev<br>
Scroll of Quiver of Marr<br>
Scroll of Scars of Sigil<br>
<br>
in return you get either the 53 air pet, boon of immolation or scintilation.<br>
<br>
in Overthere give them to Slicia J`Singe<br>
in FV give them to Hiptal Frizzleboth<br>
<br>
The turn in spells drop off of many exp giving mobs in BW, SF, Chardok, Sebilis.  they aren't worth much plat wise, so you may be able to get them pretty cheap if you auction in those zones. <p><hr>
